{"tid":398061,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一包菸為什麼有20支？","createTime":"2017-09-13T02:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T06:30:46.000Z","uid":31314,"like":8,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f774d600c03aeda27135ba0d04f840f8f850467a","tid":398061,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"一包菸為什麼有20支？<br />\n一支愛你<br />\n一支等待<br />\n一支守候<br />\n一支期待<br />\n一支渴望<br />\n一支幻想<br />\n一支難過<br />\n一支高興<br />\n一支傷心<br />\n一支孤獨<br />\n一支寂寞<br />\n一支偽裝<br />\n一支堅強<br />\n一支懦弱<br />\n一支想念<br />\n一支沉默<br />\n一支哭泣<br />\n一支微笑<br />\n一支渴望<br />\n一支無言<br />\n要把20支菸合在了一起<br />\n就是傷害和希望<br />\n隨著抽煙的姿勢<br />\n越來越熟練<br />\n愛的人也越來越隨便<br />\n男人需要香煙的陪伴<br />\n相同的有些堅強的女人也是<br />\n香煙燒掉的<br />\n是青春的眷戀<br />\n男人<br />\n走的是時光<br />\n過得是滄桑<br />\n男人會抽菸、是因為背後有故事<br />\n女人會抽菸、是因為心裡有心事<br />\n社會上<br />\n我們抽菸不是抽快樂<br />\n而是讓悲傷隨菸而去<br />\n男人抽完菸將菸蒂丟了<br />\n是把心中不愉快排除掉<br />\n男人一包菸抽完了<br />\n生活還是得照樣過<br />\n我們男人分菸給兄弟抽<br />\n並不是因為想要害了他<br />\n是因為他心中也有心事<br />\n一支菸一個故事<br />\n兩支菸多些陪伴<br />\n畫龍畫虎難畫骨<br />\n知人知面不知心<br />\n不要誤解每個會抽菸的人<br />\n#分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fl8by4vd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffl8by4vd&h=a4b6da07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"859b626bac86af556e9535e329346da411698b84","tid":398061,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"樓主幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194a74a6a3a267a1a63edb04131320ecbeadc259","tid":398061,"uid":52571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"S_Kagawa.為什麼有一點？"},{"pid":"4a5be85b019fc761e82ba1b30d3245db8c86802f","tid":398061,"uid":4895,"like":31,"dislike":7,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/101554_7d40312ba41fc3fc42e6a4df0f970c84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F101554_7d40312ba41fc3fc42e6a4df0f970c84.jpg&h=a1215797&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"689ae576cce7fa11b55c59c07d62b36092a60a28","tid":398061,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>S_Kagawa.為什麼有一點？</blockquote><br />\n柒"},{"pid":"54dc9d5081e37d4a42488290d1e8fc789bbcb051","tid":398061,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"揸刀果個邊位手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fea153bbc1edb9389d0b1b60f760a1b79dea42f","tid":398061,"uid":37604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"樓主好有才華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb85d0b64a4392b9e3b835b3186fc2b0ec03c9d","tid":398061,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好文共賞"},{"pid":"3262da9278bdb2c820d8a78b284de451955cc3e2","tid":398061,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"澳洲有40支裝<br />\n俾多廿樣黎先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69a6bd44eeef96106b5feb04402af89a2798432","tid":398061,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"我吃雪茄"},{"pid":"e45330d2cec19fb92414bb9daa81a8d690488c8c","tid":398061,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"點解會有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f218d7a6ee731a84635d01d33cd06ba69979de","tid":398061,"uid":107658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-